title: Poor Guy Seeking Prince
description: Michael is the most sought after beautician among all of the fairy tale Princesses. He helped all of them get their name and their Prince. But after years in the business, Michael wants his own Prince to come and take him away. This is an account of Michael's desperate attempts to find himself a Prince Charming, and get what he always wanted- a happily ever after.
author: Ryan Dempsey
